OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FEurope's annual music spectacle the
OL,7,FEurovision Song Contest is mixing
OL,8,Fthings up this year, holding its first
OL,9,Fever Asia edition.
OL,11,FThe Eurovision Song Contest Asia 2026
OL,12,Fhas confirmed that artists from at
OL,13,Fleast 10 countries across the
OL,14,Fcontinent will be competing: Thailand,
OL,15,FSouth Korea, the Philippines, Vietnam,
OL,16,FMalaysia, Cambodia, Laos, Bangladesh,
OL,17,FNepal and Bhutan.
OL,19,FMore countries are expected to join
OL,20,Fbefore the competition's finale, which
OL,21,Fwill take place in Bangkok in November.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
