OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FEurovision's director Martin Green
OL,7,Fsaid the expansion of the song contest
OL,8,Fmarks its 70th anniversary.
OL,10,FAnnouncing the new competition, he
OL,11,Fsaid: "As we mark the 70th anniversary
OL,12,Fof the Eurovision Song Contest, it
OL,13,Ffeels especially meaningful to open
OL,14,Fthis next chapter with Asia, a region
OL,15,Frich in culture, creativity and
OL,16,Ftalent."
OL,18,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,19,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,20,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,21,Finbox every Friday morning.
