OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FBangkok is the perfect city to host
OL,7,Fthe contest because it "has always
OL,8,Fbeen a place where cultures come
OL,9,Ftogether, where music fills the air,
OL,10,Fand where celebration is part of
OL,11,Feveryday life," said Chuwit
OL,12,FSirivajjakul, a representative of the
OL,13,FThailand Tourism Authority.
OL,15,FThe main contest, with 35 competing
OL,16,Fcountries, is scheduled to take place
OL,17,Fas usual in May. This year it will be
OL,18,Fhosted in Vienna on 16 May, after
OL,19,FAustria's entry JJ won last year's
OL,20,Fcontest with the song 'Wasted Love'.
