OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FIt is being boycotted by five
OL,7,Fcountries - Iceland, Ireland, the
OL,8,FNetherlands, Slovenia and Spain - due
OL,9,Fto criticism over Israel's
OL,10,Fparticipation, following the ongoing
OL,11,FIsrael-Hamas conflict in Gaza.
OL,13,FThousands of pro-Palestinian
OL,14,Fdemonstrators protested in Malmo,
OL,15,FSweden outside last year's competition
OL,16,Fover Israel's involvement, forcing
OL,17,Forganisers to clamp down on political
OL,18,Fflag waving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
