CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774973462
OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FThe contest has said it strives to put
OL,7,Fpop music before politics, but it has
OL,8,Frepeatedly been embroiled in world
OL,9,Fevents. Russia was expelled from the
OL,10,Fcompetition in 2022 after it invaded
OL,11,FUkraine.
OL,13,FThe main gala, run by the European
OL,14,FBroadcasting Union, draws more than
OL,15,F100 million viewers every year.
OL,17,FYouTuber and experimental singer-
OL,18,Fsongwriter Look Mum No Computer has
OL,19,Fbeen announced by the BBC as the UK's
OL,20,Frepresentative.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
