OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1774973462
OL,3,CEurovision Song Contest launches first
OL,4,Cever Asia edition
OL,6,FHe said: "I have always been a massive
OL,7,FEurovision fan, and I love the magical
OL,8,Fjoy it brings to millions of people
OL,9,Fevery year, so getting to join that
OL,10,Flegacy and fly the flag for the UK is
OL,11,Fan absolute honour that I am taking
OL,12,Fvery seriously... I will be bringing
OL,13,Fevery ounce of my creativity to my
OL,14,Fperformances, and I can't wait for
OL,15,Feveryone to hear and see what we've
OL,16,Fcreated. I hope Eurovision is ready to
OL,17,Fget synthesised!"
OL,19,FThe song he will perform at the
OL,20,Fcompetition in Austria is yet to be
OL,21,Fannounced.
